ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations and Employment Board Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Works and Government Services to be the Minister referred to in that Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2019-389 of April 26, 2019; and (2) designating the MINISTER OF PUBLIC WORKS AND GOVERNMENT SERVICES, who is not a member of the Treasury Board, to be the Minister referred to in the FEDERAL PUBLIC SECTOR LABOUR RELATIONS AND EMPLOYMENT BOARD ACT.
